msg: Initial import/prototype of the dotnet-embedder. The purpose of these components is to allow interaction between .NET and Maven. The components uses xFire for a SOAP interface to the MavenEmbedder. The MavenEmbedder is not stable enough to use, but the SOAP interface works.
